	<td width="98%">

		<table width="100%">
		<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    One Great Magician Guide!(need luclin)</b></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><A href="mailto:rabidweasel@infostations.com">Kojii</a> | 
		            11/5/2002 4:42:43 PM</b></font></p>
		         <a href="guides.asp">
		         <font face="verdana" size="2">Return to guide listing.</font></a>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Ok here's my shot at a Mage guide:<BR>
<BR>
Level. 1-3: Kill bats until they con blue to you. <BR>
<BR>
Loot: Make sure to take the bat wings cause you can sell 20 bat wings for up to 5 platinum. Keep Bone chips too. Sell everything else that drops off the bats and skellies to merchants.<BR>
<BR>
Spells:The only spells you need are the ones you start off with, summon drink and summon food. Be sure to always cast your shielding spells on yourself and always cast Burst of flame on the monster.<BR>
__________________________________________________<BR>
<BR>
Level 3-5: Kill orc pawns, fire beetles, spiderlings and stuff like that, pretty much anything that cons even(or yellow, if you have a pet)<BR>
<BR>
Loot: keep all the spiderling silks and bone chips, sell all the other loot to merchants. when you have 20 of either Spiderling silks or Bone chips, shout &quot;WTS stack of spiderling silks, pst&quot;(WTS means Want To Sell and pst means Please Send Tells.) you can get around 3 pp for those. <BR>
<BR>
Spells:Be sure to buy all your Elementalkins once you get to level 4, they REALLY help. also get Fire flux, Gate, and Summon Bandages.Gate teleports you back to your bind point, Fire flux is a better version of Burst of Flame, and Summon Bandages is self explanatory. <BR>
__________________________________________________<BR>
<BR>
Level 5-8: Head to either Orc hill in greater faydark(ask for directions) or East Commonlands, which is one zone over from West Freeport. get a group with a warrior or a ranger if your on Orc hill, and kill Orc Centurions. In EC(East Commonlands) Kill Bears and Leaf scarabs, and anything that cons even to you.<BR>
<BR>
Loot: If you get any rusty items give them to your pet, otherwise if your pet already has one sell them to merchants.<BR>
<BR>
Spells: Your lvl 8 spells, well you need to get your new pets!Get all of your Elemantalings, Eye of Zomm, Flame bolt, Renew Elements(a great pet healing spell),Lesser shielding, shield of fire, and shock of blades.<BR>
__________________________________________________<BR>
<BR>
Levels 8-12: No matter what race you are you should head to The Northern desert of Ro(ask for directions) And kill Spiders, Scarabs, and the like. At 10 Get in a dervish group until you get to level 12.<BR>
<BR>
Loot: Pretty much sell everything you loot to merchants.<BR>
<BR>
Spells: You gotta get your new Elementals(again, yay!), Burnout(a pet buff), Rain of blades, Ward summoned and Cancel Magic.<BR>
__________________________________________________<BR>
<BR>
Levels 12-15: Go to the freeport boat docks. Get on the boat and after you get into the ocean of tears wait on the boat until you see the big rocks on either side of the boat.Jump off the boat and get onto the one on the right. Kill the sirens until you ding 15.<BR>
<BR>
Loot: Sell everything you loot to merchants(which is only mermaid scales).<BR>
<BR>
Spells: You might wanna get your lvl 16 spells beforehand because now your gonna travel to the moon and wont be able to buy any there. get all your new Minor summon pets, Shielding, and Shock of Flame.<BR>
__________________________________________________<BR>
<BR>
Levels 15-22: One word:Paludal. This place is no joke, Major exp here, I got 8 levels (14-22) in one saturday, no lie. Go to the moon(ask directions) and then ask someone directions to the Paludal Caverns.Once you get there try to get into a Bandit 2 group, otherwise the other camps are ok.1 thing, when running around there, Invisibility yourself, cause alot of things will attack you.<BR>
__________________________________________________<BR>
<BR>
Loot: theres ok loot, but its too heavy and you dont want to be cucumbered(I know its encumbered, but hey.)<BR>
<BR>
Spells: get your lvl 20 pets by going to the Ocean of tears, getting off at the first island(coming from freeport), and swimming to another island that is strait ahead, theres a merchant in these little ruins that will sell your lvl 20 pets to you there.<BR>
<BR>
Levels 22-24: Try to get a group in Marus Seru(ask directions from the nexus)<BR>
__________________________________________________<BR>
<BR>
Im currently still in marus seru, Well, GL(good luck) to you all, if you have any questions email me at rabidweasel@infostations.com or send a tell to Kojii On the bertoxxulous server<BR>
<BR>
Kojii<BR>
Lvl 23 Mage of Karana<BR>
Bertox server.
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
